n Trace 1, sustained time is dominated by moving operand and result bytes through HBM; kernels that move those bytes faster therefore finish each invocation sooner without changing the math.\n\n**Impact estimate:**\n\n- Low end (75% gap target): 0.075 ms savings (26.79% E2E)\n- High end (100% gap target): 0.10 ms savings (35.72% E2E)\n- Range: 0.075–0.10 ms (26.79–35.72% E2E)\n","message":"The file /home/AMD/khoffmey/dev/TraceLens/evals/unit_tests_comparative/test02_attention_both_unfused/analysis_output_ref/category_findings/gemm_findings.md has been updated."}}}}},{"toolCall":{"editToolCall":{"result":{"error":{"path":"","error":"The string to replace was not found in the file.","modelVisibleError":"The string to replace was not found in the file (even after relaxing whitespace). Found a possible fuzzy match, did you mean:\nCopyright (c) 2024 - 2025 Advanced Micro Devices, Inc. All rights reserved.\n\nSee LICENSE for license information.\n-->\n"}}}}},{"toolCall":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/home/AMD/khoffmey/dev/TraceLens/evals/unit_tests_comparative/test02_attention_both_unfused/analysis_output_ref/category_findings/gemm_findings.md","offset":55},"result":{"success":{"content":"\n**Identification:** The row was flagged from aligned **GPU kernel time**: Trace 1 totals exceed Trace 2 for the same op name, shapes, and invocation counts on the comparative pairing. The op is **memory-bound** on Trace 1. No **`fusion_flagged: true`** appears in `gemm_metrics.json` for this category. (source: `gemm_metrics.json` → `operations[].time_ms`, `operations[].efficiency.bound_type`, `operations[].efficiency.resolved_peak_hbm_bw`, `gemm_ops.csv` → `lca_total_kernel_time_trace1_us`, `lca_total_kernel_time_trace2_us`, `delta_us (trace2 - trace1)`)\n\n**Data:**\n\n| Operation | Trace 1 Time (ms) | Trace 2 Time (ms) | Count (T1/T2) | Difference (ms) | FLOPS/Byte (T1) | Bound (T1) |\n|-----------|-------------------|-------------------|---------------|-----------------|---------